column5: Had a great trip up to the superior tribs this spring, the water was high and the run was just starting this day we 3 to 4 inches of snow but the fishing was still "hot"
hey moosemeat, is that troutologist and myself standing in that last photo? small world and that was definitely a hot day.
Right on moosemeat Beauty steel!!!! congratulations Leechman
Thats us for sure in the last pic. What a day!!  I assume Im catching a fish or cursing about just losing one.
Ya thats the three of you, i emailed a larger pic of you guys on the river, what a day!! maybe we'll see ya next year!!
Love the pics...I'm dying to get up that way for steel.  Thanks for sharing.
